# read_theory_cluster_improve.md

## File
utils/theory-cluster/theory_cluster_improve.py

---

## 1. Purpose

Transform raw cluster outputs into report-ready audit-grade governance text.

Reads:
utils/theory-cluster/output/cluster/<DOMAIN>_theory_cluster_output.json

Writes:
utils/theory-cluster/output/improved/<DOMAIN>_theory_improved_output.json

Focus:
- Formal audit tone
- Structured paragraphs
- Deterministic JSON output
- Cache-driven cost control

---

## 2. Architecture Overview

Cluster output JSON
   ↓
Function 1 – Context_Initial aggregation
   ↓
Function 2 – Evaluation_Initial extraction
   ↓
Function 3 – Details_Initial aggregation
   ↓
Function 4 – Join arrays
   ↓
Function 5 – AI rewrite (parallel + cached)
   ↓
Improved output JSON

---

## 3. Input / Output Paths

### Input
utils/theory-cluster/output/cluster/<DOMAIN>_theory_cluster_output.json

### Output
utils/theory-cluster/output/improved/<DOMAIN>_theory_improved_output.json

### Cache
utils/theory-cluster/_cache/<DOMAIN>_theory_improve_cache.json

---

## 4. Functional Breakdown

### Function 1 – Context_Initial

- Filters decision_tree rows
- Score == 1
- Question Q1–Q6
- Aggregates distinct Objective values

Returns:
[Domain, Context_Initial]

---

### Function 2 – Evaluation_Initial

- decision_tree rows
- Question == Q1
- Score 0–5
- Returns:
  Domain
  Score
  Action_Code
  Text

---

### Function 3 – Details_Initial

- action_catalog rows
- Groups by Action_Code
- Preserves procedure ordering
- Concatenates procedural definitions

---

### Function 4 – Join

Join grain:
Domain + Score + Action_Code

Produces unified item:
{
  Domain,
  Score,
  Action_Code,
  Action_Title,
  Context_Initial,
  Evaluation_Initial,
  Details_Initial,
  Procedures
}

---

### Function 5 – AI Improvement

Uses strict JSON system prompt:

{
  "context": "...",
  "evaluation": "...",
  "details": "..."
}

Constraints:
- context = exactly 3 paragraphs
- evaluation = exactly 4 paragraphs
- details = exactly 4 paragraphs
- No bullets
- No markdown
- No commentary

---

## 5. Fingerprint Strategy

Fingerprint includes:

- Domain
- Score
- Action_Code
- Action_Title
- Context_Initial
- Evaluation_Initial
- Details_Initial

If any input changes → regeneration occurs.

---

## 6. Performance Controls

DEFAULT_MODEL_IMPROVE = gpt-4o-mini  
DEFAULT_MAX_WORKERS = 6  
DEFAULT_BATCH_SIZE = 12  

Parallel:
ThreadPoolExecutor

Batch-based saving to prevent loss.

---

## 7. CLI Parameters

--mode all | domain  
--domain DG  
--model gpt-4o-mini  
--max-workers  
--batch-size  
--clear-cache  

---

## 8. Execution

Run all domains:
python theory_cluster_improve.py

Run single domain:
python theory_cluster_improve.py --mode domain --domain DG

Force regeneration:
python theory_cluster_improve.py --clear-cache

